title: Firefox 121.0.1 (64-bit) invalid file format error on youtube upload
content:
Hello

I'm unable to upload even that videos what was already successfully uploaded some times ago. I using Microsoft Edge now to upload on youtube and it is fine with all my videos. Hope you can fix soon.

title: Cannot print all pages using firefox (graphics are blank) whereas different browser no problem.
content: If emails contain graphics or pictures Firefox just shows/print a blank area. The messages (wording) of the body of the email prints fine. Different browsers prints fine, thus in order to print I have to use a different browser and prints fine. Why is Firefox not permitting this? Same thing with certain pdf's, it doesn't access it but other browsers are fine. I use Windows 10. Thanks
creator: vercp
